    * improve colors
    * remove the material_drawer_ prefix and allow setting the color by the normal attributes OR prefixed attributes
    
    SAMPLE changing the primary color:
        <color name="primary">#2196F3</color>
    or
        <color name="material_drawer_primary">#2196F3</color>
    
    if you overwrite both the prefixed variant will win

